Revert "Update README.md"

This reverts commit fdb58bdb1d10f3b75704dd20ed3c132bf1dc4f3b.
Update README.md
Add badge
Add proper default name argument for cytoscape demo endpoint. Closes #145.
Add missing test dep so builds succeed again.
Add a random fun config example for some other uses.
Make example configs more consistent, convert plotly example to fixed layout.
Remove arguments check in promise gathering callback as it's unecessary.
Monkeypatch delete-all in existing test to prevent real deletion.
Add datatable only config.
Add support for new d3-flamegraph chart.
Add wordcloud utils, tests, docs, and small ui tweaks.
Fix some cli tests.
Doc updates.
Use better scaling for numbergroup type.
Fix regression in style where row color was conflicting with draggable/droppable styles.
Fix link to screenshot
Fix json example
Add new widget type - number grouping. Closes #131.
Fix colliding id in example configs.
Add delete-all cli command and test, add categories to fixture data.
Make style and text for 'add row' ui clearer to user in edit mode.
Move misc. utility type functions into a utils module, update tests.
Move some schema checking functions into the schema module for better organization, and update tests.
Remove console log.
Fix a bug when getting cached data where the number of promises is only 1 and the wrong index is used.
Fix bug when trying to split query params that don't exist in js util.
Update docs.

Allow the ability to group charts by category. Closes #135

    - Fix an issue where parsing raw config in demo mode could break the layout when the field data was empty.
    - Add some more tests to increase coverage.
    - Move request variables back into view so unit testing out-of-scope function works again,
        add more robustness when categorizing views.
    - Fix some tests.
    - Add initial code to create and manage categories in dashboards.
Fix path issue and cleanup some code in dump_fixtures util.
Move some section around for clearer/easier quickstart intro. Closes #137.
Make a test check more explicit, Monkeypatch a method in mongo tests to prevent timeout issues in travisci.
Remove console log.
Fix a bug where urls that are not json mime-type will be loaded incorrectly during url aggregation. Fixes #136.
Add missing support for individually handling errors when grouping ajax requests.

Add shared url feature and url aggregration for performance. Closes #132

Specific changes:

- Add test coverage for new utils
- Add support for dumping and loading fixtures via CLI and Make.
- Add docs for new feature.
- Add example endpoint and config for shared data, and use shared key if it exists when loading cached data or
    reloading regular json.
- Implement url caching on initial load for duplicate urls.
- Fully remove need for separate loadWidgetData function.
- Move widget load function to widget object, fix references and cleanup some code.
Remove css from linting for codeclimate config.
Remove tests from scoring
Add a bullet point to readme.
Add missing doc string values.
Add handler update for d3 datatable height issue. Addresses #125.
Add new data utils.
Add some contributing notes.
